00:19:47.387 --> 00:19:49.957 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Rohan] <i>I need to get out</i>
 <i>of this place immediately.</i>

00:19:51.759 --> 00:19:53.427 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I need to escape.</i>

00:19:55.663 --> 00:19:59.466 position:13% line:83% align:start
