00:20:40.608 --> 00:20:44.212 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>has turned into the god,</i>
 <i>Hermes, incarnate.</i>

00:20:44.244 --> 00:20:46.814 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I shouldn't have</i>
 <i>gone anywhere near him.</i>

00:20:46.848 --> 00:20:48.750 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I risked my life</i>
 <i>and our competition</i>

00:20:48.783 --> 00:20:49.650 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>for that remote.</i>

